@startuml developer-onboarding
title Developer Onboarding — Register in PaymentSplitter

skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam participantBackgroundColor #FFF3E0
skinparam participantBorderColor #FF9800

actor "Developer" as Dev
participant "PaymentSplitter\nContract (Arc)" as Contract
participant "Arc Network" as Arc
participant "Developer Service\n(withPaywall)" as Service

== One-Time Setup ==

Dev -> Arc : Call register(walletAddress)\non PaymentSplitter contract

Arc -> Contract : Execute register()
Contract -> Contract : Store: developer[walletAddress] = {\n  registered: true,\n  balance: 0\n}
Contract -> Dev : ✅ Registration confirmed\n(tx hash)

== Middleware Integration ==

Dev -> Service : Install @universal-paywall/middleware\n\nnpm install @universal-paywall/middleware

Dev -> Service : Configure:\n\nwithPaywall(handler, {\n  price: '0.01',        // USD\n  developerId: '0xDev...', // registered wallet\n  network: 'arc-mainnet'   // optional, default\n})

note over Service : Contract address for arc-mainnet\nbaked into middleware package.\nNo API key needed.

== Balance Check & Withdrawal ==

Dev -> Contract : getBalance(walletAddress)
Contract -> Dev : { balance: "50000000" } // micro-USDC

Dev -> Contract : withdraw(amount)
Contract -> Contract : Verify caller == registered wallet\nCheck balance >= amount
Contract -> Dev : Transfer USDC → wallet

@enduml
